column3: “Solid indica, not quite middle of the road but not mind blowing. Just a solid above average indica with an interesting smell and taste.”

“Killer bud, never been more relaxed, best nights sleep.... EVER??!?  I've got a new item in my medicine cabinet!  Movie, snacks & my pillow, work by my side as it leaves me still totally functional, in love... WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN ALL MY LIFE!?”
